{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_06_01",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 06 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――すみれが帰郷して一週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One week after Sumire returned home",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 2.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、お母さん、お兄ちゃん。掃除は終わったよ\n空の桶も洗っておいたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Mom‚ big brother. I finished cleaning.\nI also washed the empty barrels.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2,
      "endTime": 9.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrmom001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、今朝も早いのね\nもっとゆっくりしてもいいのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My‚ you're up early again this morning.\nYou can sleep in a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1,
      "endTime": 16.4680723508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrbro001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれは力仕事なんてしなくていいから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ you don't have to do heavy lifting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6666666667,
      "endTime": 20.4333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの。お父さんが入院して大変なのに\nそんなのんきなこと言ってられないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? Dad is hospitalized and things are tough‚\nso I can't just relax!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6333333333,
      "endTime": 28.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrbro002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お前……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "endTime": 30.900000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "だから～、私は奥山酒造の跡取り娘なの！\n私はこうして、お兄ちゃんの手伝いが出来て嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm telling you~‚ I'm the future successor of Okuyama Brewery!\nI'm happy to help you like this‚ big brother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1,
      "endTime": 40.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "家の仕事を手伝いながら、地元の学校に通って……\nこういう生活も楽しいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Helping out with the family business‚ attending the local school…\nThis kind of life is fun too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1666666667,
      "endTime": 48.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そのうちお兄ちゃんの仕事全部とっちゃうかもね！\nあ、朝ごはんの前に玄関の掃除もしてこよっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might even take over all of your work someday‚ big brother!\nAh‚ I'll clean the entrance before breakfast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2666666667,
      "endTime": 57.1666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9100.000000000002,
          "startTime": 57.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 52.8000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrbro003.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれ、お前は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sumire‚ you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3666666667,
      "endTime": 63.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7366.6666665999965,
          "startTime": 64.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 64.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 64.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、今日もいっぱい働いたな～\nって、あ、いてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I worked hard again today\nOw‚ ow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6,
      "endTime": 74.60000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 70.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 74.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "うう、筋肉痛……体力には自信があったんだけど\nダンスとは違う筋肉使うから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ muscle soreness… I was confident in my stamina‚\nbut I guess I use different muscles for dancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8,
      "endTime": 84.60000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 85.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃん\n今頃どうしてるかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui-chan and Yu-chan‚\nI wonder how they're doing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0666666667,
      "endTime": 90.3666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 90.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "私から連絡は、今更出来ないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's too late for me to contact them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6,
      "endTime": 94.76666666669999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9700.000000000004,
          "startTime": 100.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 94.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "二人には、私の分まで頑張ってもらいたいな……\n――ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope they're working hard‚ for my sake too…\n――Hmm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9666666667,
      "endTime": 101.39999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 100.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrmom002.m4a",
      "text": "あの子、やっぱり無理してるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That child‚ she's definitely pushing herself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8666666667,
      "endTime": 107.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 107.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrbro004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、見ていて辛いよ\n俺達の前では無理に明るく振る舞って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's painful to watch.\nShe's putting on a brave face in front of us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3,
      "endTime": 114.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrbro005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれは今まで俺の夢をサポートしてくれてたのに\n俺はすみれの夢を守れなかった。情けないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire has been supporting my dream all this time‚\nbut I couldn't protect her dream. I'm pathetic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4333333333,
      "endTime": 126.4805613199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 126.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "（お兄ちゃん……そんな風に思ってたんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Big brother… you were thinking that way.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6666666667,
      "endTime": 131.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 131.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrmom003.m4a",
      "text": "……それは、私達、親の責任よ\nごめんね。二人の夢を、守ってあげられなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's our fault‚ as parents.\nI'm sorry. For not being able to protect both your dreams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4333333333,
      "endTime": 142.06666666659999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 23099.999999999993,
          "startTime": 154.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smrbro006.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ。元々、俺が留学したいなんて言い出さなければ\nすみれに負担を掛けずに済んだ。全部、俺が悪いんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. If I hadn't said I wanted to study abroad‚\nSumire wouldn't have had to shoulder that burden. It's all my fault.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2666666667,
      "endTime": 153.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14500,
          "startTime": 156.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamahall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 154.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 156.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 156.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言わないで！\nお兄ちゃんは何も悪くないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't say that!\nYou didn't do anything wrong‚ big brother!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7,
      "endTime": 163.1333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 163.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
